Interface IServerExecutor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttrInfoSenderExecutor, AvailableDatExecutor, ConnectionCloserExecutor, ConvertExecutor, DatabaseExecutor, LoadTreeExecutor, PredictionExecutor, SendMailExecutor, SupportedExtExecutor, TreeSerializerExecutor, UploadExecutor, ValidateMailExecutor

    public interface IServerExecutor
    According to the "Command" design pattern, this interface represents the way in order to execute a specific operation to satisfy a specific request.
